FLATGANGO MOVIE TICKETING APP
Flatdango is a web application that allows users to purchase movie tickets from Flatiron Movie Theater. The app fetches data from a local server running a JSON DB server and provides features such as viewing movie details, a menu of all movies, and buying tickets.

Table of Contents
-Features
-Requirements
-Project Setup
-Usage
-Core Deliverables
-Bonus Deliverables
-Extra Bonus
-Contributing

FEATURES
-Display details for a specific movie.
-Show a menu of all movies.
-Buy tickets for a movie.
REQUIREMENTS

Node.js
JSON DB server
PROJECT SETUP

Clone the repository.
Install: npm install
Start the local JSON DB server: json-server --watch db.json
Open index.html in a web browser.

USAGE
-Open the app in a web browser.
-View movie details by clicking on a movie in the menu.
-Buy tickets for a movie using the "Buy Ticket" button.

CORE DELIVERABLES
-See the first movie's details on page load.
-View a menu of all movies on the left side of the page.
-Buy a ticket for a movie.

BONUS DELIVERABLES
-Click on a movie in the menu to replace the currently displayed movie's details.
-Indicate a sold-out movie by changing the button text to "Sold Out."

EXTRA BONUS
-Persist the updated number of tickets sold on the server.
-Delete a film from the server.
